    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. Mechanically, it starts up every time and runs consistently, but you should expect some minor fluid seeps and a suspension that feels a bit loose on rougher roads. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some paint fading on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear and some staining from years of use. It\u2019s a solid, functional car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
      "price": 18500.0,
