    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! It honestly breaks my heart a little to post this, but it\u2019s time for this absolute beauty to find a new home. I\u2019ve treated this car like a member of the family\u2014it\u2019s in stunning, showroom-ready shape and drives just as smooth as the day I got it. You\u2019ll be hard-pressed to find another one this clean and well-loved; it's truly the pride of my garage. It\u2019s a real head-turner that\u2019s ready for many more miles of smiles. Come by, have a coffee, and take a look; you\u2019re going to fall in love just like I did!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
