      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a pristine example of the S65-powered E92. This unit features a surgically precise 7-speed M-DCT gearbox with lightning-fast actuation. The high-revving 4.0L V8 has been meticulously maintained with a rigorous lubrication schedule to ensure peak compression across all cylinders. We\u2019ve addressed the common S65 pain points\u2014rod bearings have been treated with high-performance shells and throttle actuators are reinforced. The chassis remains incredibly taut, benefiting from EDC-calibrated damping that provides a zero-compromise interface between the asphalt and the driver. Paint depth is consistent across all panels, showing a mirror finish that rivals factory delivery. This isn't just a car; it's a mechanically optimized masterpiece ready for the purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
