    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine the sun setting over the coast as you glide effortlessly in this automotive masterpiece. This isn't just a car; it's a time capsule of elegance, finished in a deep, lustrous hue that captures every passing glance. Inside, the cabin welcomes you with the rich, intoxicating aroma of hand-stitched leather and polished wood, whispering stories of grand adventures yet to be lived. Every curve of its silhouette reflects a legacy of craftsmanship, offering a driving experience that feels less like transportation and more like a private symphony. It possesses a rare, undeniable charisma that demands attention, promising its next custodian a journey filled with grace and unparalleled style.",
      "price": 48900.0,
