    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to be listing my pride and joy, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this absolute gem. I\u2019ve babied this car since the day I got it\u2014always garage-kept, hand-washed every Sunday, and treated like a member of the family. It\u2019s in truly stunning shape, looking and smelling like it just left the showroom. You might find a microscopic pebble chip if you use a magnifying glass, but to anyone else, she\u2019s flawless. She drives smooth as silk and is ready for a new adventure. Come take a look and let's get you behind the wheel of something special!",
