    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered here is a masterclass in automotive refinement. This unit features a high-compression, naturally aspirated powerplant with optimized volumetric efficiency and zero-lash valvetrain tolerances. The drivetrain is anchored by a torque-sensing limited-slip differential and a short-throw shifter with precision-milled bushings for surgical gear engagement. The chassis has been treated to a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and runs on a bespoke coilover setup tuned for neutral handling and high-speed stability. Every fluid change has been documented using high-ester synthetics to ensure maximum thermal protection. The exterior boasts a deep-lustre finish with a multi-stage ceramic coating, preserving the aerodynamic profile. This is a turn-key machine for the discerning driver who demands mechanical purity and zero parasitic loss.",
